Dialogs.Text: LostDecipher2: Interesting, the visit log here is public.
LostDecipher2: Did you made it public?
MsMaki95: Nope. Was like this when we came here. Like i said, we didn't touched this room much.
LostDecipher2: Interesting, and for the visits log... We have really old visitors from the old days, meaning this room is not new at all.
MsMaki95: I see, can you recognize someone?
LostDecipher2: No, a lot of people look like users i didn't even met. This chat had a lot of users in it's time.
MsMaki95: I see. Interesting, we can see the history of the chat form things like this. This is exciting.
LostDecipher2: Still, recent visits here were only... 5 users, counting me of course.
MsMaki95: So... What does that mean.
LostDecipher2: Means that, since you came here, no unknown user came to this room to do something.
MsMaki95: That's good to know, we didn't wanted this place becoming too public.
Thomas B: (This is strange though, there is an user, 'Worldo', that entered to this room way before this 5 users but... A year or two after this chat closed.)
